
This is a full stack application that allow users make an account and sell or borrow books from other users on this app.
The application keeps track of book ownership by scanning the isbn of the book with a google API.

You can search for books by user names, book names, or book description. The application can also suggest book genres based on 
previous book searches.

The application keeps track of which books you have borrowed from who, and which books has you lent out to.

You can also edit your profile setting such as putting a picture, phone number, and email.



To use this application run the code folder in iBOOKit on android studio.
